Package ru.nsu.khamidullin.pizza

Class PizzeriaConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nsu.khamidullin.pizza.PizzeriaConfiguration
  • public class PizzeriaConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    The PizzeriaConfiguration class represents the configuration parameters for a simulated pizzeria. It includes information such as bakers' cooking times, delivery capacities, and storage capacity.
